            <p>Carpet fibers act as a magnet for dirt, traffic soot, pet dander, pollen, and dust mites. Standard vacuuming removes surface debris, but leaves deep-rooted contaminants trapped inside the pile.</p>
            <p>Our professional carpet service utilizes advanced hot water extraction technology. By infusing high-temperature water (110°C) with eco-friendly cleaning agents, we break down stubborn soils, emulsify grease, and rinse them out with dual-motor vacuum suction.</p>
